{"tid":1888521,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"自己諗野好極端好偏激 點算好？","createTime":"2020-02-20T08:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T16:43:51.000Z","uid":307755,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6bdae2ebd52d865082d4a5d9eaad44b10eaad6c3","tid":1888521,"uid":307755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:58:19.000Z","msg":"所有野發生我都只會走向兩個極端<br />\n有時搞到身邊嘅人都好似好辛苦咁 <br />\n特別係我男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n例如：<br />\n人哋對我有少少評價<br />\n我就會覺得自己真係好差好垃圾<br />\n覺得人哋好唔鍾意我<br />\n一直陷左入去 瘋狂鑽牛角尖 <br />\n到最後好似係我做錯野咁令到身體既人都唔開心<br />\n<br />\n真係好對唔住佢地 方法會令到我個人冇咁敏感<br />\n定係還是我去睇下醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7dfd82ae4c57b6af536c144c63ceec67f54b0c","tid":1888521,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"我係你男朋友就搵過另一條女"},{"pid":"0050c03b8721db0a2f756cde86eeed6a1739f757","tid":1888521,"uid":195257,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4576aa3240b7a229a555297eaca7ea158fd7a2","tid":1888521,"uid":307755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7dfd82ae4c57b6af536c144c63ceec67f54b0c","tid":1888521,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:59:43.000Z","msg":"我係你男朋友就搵過另一條女"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T09:01:57.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過令到佢辛苦不如放過佢 <br />\n我最想既係放過自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係好想同佢行到最後"},{"pid":"479e36a1d085e42f4260d7d755c5dfa9d01f1e88","tid":1888521,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f4576aa3240b7a229a555297eaca7ea158fd7a2","tid":1888521,"uid":307755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ba7dfd82ae4c57b6af536c144c63ceec67f54b0c","tid":1888521,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-20T08:59:43.000Z","msg